# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/).

## [UNRELEASED]
These features have not yet been released but they are planned for future updates.
- CentralAuth Lock/Hide Function
- Global Account Information
- !protect Command
- !rollback Command

## [1.0.0] 
### Added
- Channel Operator tools in bot.py
- Added Action Logging Support
- CentralAuth lookup function

### Changed
- !blockuser now allows multiword reasons
- !unblockuser now allows multiword reasons
- !delete now allows multiword reasons
- !log now allows multiword messages

### Fixed
This update also includes bug fixes and other improvements. This update:
- Fixed a bug where !log command would not connect to the API
- Fixed a bug where !delete did not have proper credentials

### Security
- Fixed a bug that where the bot did not check if the IRC user was logged in
- For more information please see https://github.com/examknow/MH-WikiBot/security/advisories/GHSA-7hf3-wvp8-34r9
